# Client React

## Structure

One folder per component: `Component.jsx`, `Component.css`, `index.js` barrel.

- Import via `@/` alias and barrels (`@/components`, `@/hooks`, `@/pages`, `@/api`)

## Data Fetching

1. Hooks in `client/src/hooks/api/` (`useApiQuery`, `useApiMutation`)
2. API modules: `blogApi`, `adminApi`, `commentApi`
3. No raw `axios` in page components

Migrate away from `AppContext` for new features — use hooks.

## Ant Design

Sole UI library: `antd` + `@ant-design/icons`.

- Prefer existing components (`Table`, `Form`, `Modal`, `Card`, `Layout`) over custom UI
- Theme tokens from `client/src/App.jsx` — use `theme.useToken()`, not hardcoded colors
- Toasts: `react-hot-toast`; everything else: Ant Design
- Sanitize HTML with DOMPurify; edit rich text with Quill

## Constants & i18n

- Routes: `client/src/constants/routes.js`
- API paths: `client/src/constants/apiEndpoints.js`
- User strings: `client/src/i18n/locales/en.json` via `useTranslation()`

## Do Not

- Add MUI, Chakra, shadcn, or other UI libraries
- Add `console.log` in committed code
- Introduce Redux/Zustand — use existing hooks layer
